**原标题：**SCP-691-FR Papillomavirus
**原作者：** [[user Honamii]]
**原作发布日期：** 11/05/2024
**图片来源：**[https://www.rawpixel.com/image/6287330/png-sticker-vintage seringue]
[https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?search=butterfly+white+background&title=Special:MediaSearch&type=image papillon]
